Description.4: The Johnstown Farmers' Market is an open air market in the heart of the city. Guests may purchase fresh locally grown produce and flowers as well as a variety of prepared foods, baked goods, and handcrafted items.
Description.33: The Main Street Farmers Market strives to provide the greater Honesdale community with access to superb local products. The Market is a vibrant and friendly gathering of exemplary local producers and enthusiastic consumers, connecting through a mutual appreciation for each other and for our regional foodscape.
